  "title": "A filter change event needs to be emitted",
  "body": "I have a fair amount of custom code which allows for graceful mobile rendering of search results with their filters.\n\nThis all works great until I click on a filter, at which point the view is re-rendered and the bindings of my jQuery are lost etc. I wouldn't mind except that I have no way to destruct my plugins and re-construct.\n\nMaybe `render` should be called again?\n",
